{"tid":2074673,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"我預左無乜人睇呢到","createTime":"2020-06-22T09:29:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T06:12:53.000Z","uid":191654,"like":9,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9fdf996bb9260ef96cee308073a7e537192e9d5c","tid":2074673,"uid":191654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T09:29:23.000Z","msg":"大家日日都係到睇疫症新聞，日程表，我諗呢樹應該無人會再睇<br />\n<br />\n但我都要搏一鋪，就好似香港人而家咁樣，其實大家都係為緊自己嘅生活、自由拼搏中。<br />\n<br />\n#喜歡的請轉發<br />\n#替身邊香港人加油<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;We Offer Respect, Love &amp; Dream&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n世界快要塌下，前程尚有幾萬里，唯有尊重、愛和夢想，支撐著孤島上每個人的信念，低窪總有天跨過。<br />\n<br />\n《到世界塌下》<br />\n<br />\n曲：喬 @享樂團<br />\n詞：黃綺琳<br />\n編：享樂團<br />\n監：享樂團 /家豪 @Ever<br />\n<br />\n烽煙接近　天空晦暗<br />\n即將戰爭　你卻設法安寢<br />\n當天信任　都給軟禁<br />\n孤島已不斷的陸沉<br />\n<br />\n其實我們　各自有些牽掛<br />\n全城危難　怎說綿綿情話<br />\n<br />\n這世界快要塌下<br />\n被風吹雨打<br />\n城牆沒有護蔭　被追趕跌進低窪<br />\n你與我放棄對話<br />\n未體恤我嗎<br />\n誰曾被愛亦會　像滄海急於變化<br />\n共聚都要怕　病毒失控嗎<br />\n逐漸遠離<br />\n今日　是末日嗎<br />\n<br />\n分開以後　親身見證<br />\n不肯覺醒　你怕會變孤星<br />\n一起抗命 　一起好勝<br />\n推翻我當日的罪名<br />\n<br />\n然後我們　放下那些感性<br />\n茫茫人海　跟我繼續旅程<br />\n<br />\n到世界快要塌下<br />\n若風吹雨打<br />\n仍然沒有護蔭　就相擁撐過低窪<br />\n聽世界冷血責罵<br />\n就擊倒我嗎<br />\n前程尚有萬里　就牽手急促進化<br />\n日落中記掛　浪漫的戲碼<br />\n與我築起一個家　要有你吧<br />\n到世界快要塌下<br />\n若風吹雨打<br />\n仍然沒有護蔭　就相擁撐過低窪<br />\n聽世界冷血責罵<br />\n就擊倒我嗎<br />\n前程尚有萬里　就牽手急促進化<br />\n共渡這剎那　浪漫的戲碼<br />\n現實照常　崩壞　並未害怕<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n《到世界塌下》 已於各大音樂平台上架<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n主唱Vocalist：旨呈@享樂團<br />\n鼓手Drummer: Samuel Wong@享樂團<br />\n琴手Keyboardist : 阿喬@享樂團<br />\n結他手Guitarist：Addy Tsoi@享樂團<br />\n低音結他手Bassist：Keath Kong<br />\n和音Backing Vocalist：旨呈@享樂團<br />\n和音Backing Vocalist：家豪 @Ever <br />\n錄音工程師Recording Engineer：Addy Tsoi, Soda Lam<br />\n錄音室Recording Studio：Wave Music Studio 浪潮音樂<br />\n混音Mixing &amp; Mastering : Gabriel Cheung<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n服裝贊助：Adidas Originals / Timberland <br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n#享樂團 #到世界塌下 #記錄 #愛 #尊重 #夢想 #獅子山下  #黃綺琳 #3THINK #前程尚有幾萬里 #加油 #香港人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《到世界塌下》youtube ￼影片Link :<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/oBm6E2w86EQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FoBm6E2w86EQ&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0FyPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=f9ac33bb\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/oBm6E2w86EQ</a>"},{"pid":"4539a3da58e1243e6f794c2f9e5166facd62fa66","tid":2074673,"uid":77717,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T09:30:09.000Z","msg":"支持本地音樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0956a011820296760aad75d164687ea3b6c01e64","tid":2074673,"uid":191654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4539a3da58e1243e6f794c2f9e5166facd62fa66","tid":2074673,"uid":77717,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T09:30:09.000Z","msg":"支持本地音樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T10:43:27.000Z","msg":"朵謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1d6064406cb284a29f736b497698c5041fad808","tid":2074673,"uid":191654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T15:31:13.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"9fbe5a17fdb91ba09bbfac54e29fad9d36284f8e","tid":2074673,"uid":63361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T17:08:59.000Z","msg":"幫你推一推"},{"pid":"305960a60b874da6d4492c26687886dc15167618","tid":2074673,"uid":191654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9fbe